responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "2309573147AE843CC6192489C271BAA6", "Forged in the high halls of Aela, this sword is a relic most ornate, its form betraying a purpose not for mortal hand. So finely wrought is its balance, that none but the chosen may wield it, for to all others it is but dead weight. Upon its edge, in script old as moonlight, are these words inscribed: \"Excellio Tri\'Sanctus. Arm Un\'Varrow, Suum\'Luna.\" Let he who would draw it know, this is no common steel, but a bond sworn in shadow and sanctity.")
name: CSQ_DD_0028_ETS_Sword_ExcellioTriSanctus_3
